intent.user_query: What are the top 5 products with the highest total revenue generated from sales, and what was their total revenue?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductName, SUM(sd.Quantity * sd.UnitPrice) AS TotalRevenue FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON sd.ProductID = p.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY TotalRevenue DESC LIMIT 5;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductName, SUM(sd.Quantity * sd.UnitPrice) AS TotalRevenue FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON sd.ProductID = p.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY TotalRevenue DESC LIMIT 5;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
